Austria to Sue Czech, Slovak Nuclear Plants, Oesterreich Reports

-- B y   Z o e   S c h n e e w e i s s
-- 
2011-03-22T07:16:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/austria-to-sue-czech-slovak-nuclear-plants-oesterreich-reports.html
Austria ’s government will today
decide an “anti nuclear action plan,” which includes law suits
at the European court against the nuclear power plants in
Temelin in the  Czech Republic  and Mochovce in Slovakia,
Oesterreich newspaper reported, without saying where it got the
information.  The two power plants are on the border to Austria, the paper
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Zoe Schneeweiss at 
 zschneeweiss@bloomberg.net  